## purpose
Defines core runtime handling for economy.

## runtime_scope
Runtime covers economic visibility,
value-flow-aware display,
restricted-flow rendering,
historical economic reference,
and safe failure rendering.

## validation_rules
- economic context must resolve
- value-flow basis must resolve
- participant scope must resolve
- disclosure scope must be valid

## failure_modes
- invalid economic context
- invalid value-flow basis
- invalid participant scope
- safe runtime fallback

## observability
Runtime must emit enough signals
to distinguish active flow,
restricted flow,
historical reference,
and failure surface.

## review_checklist
- economy runtime scope is explicit
- flow-aware rendering is explicit
- failure handling is explicit
